HEADWORD: yuck factor
<hw>yuck factor</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>a reaction of repugnance or
distaste; -- used in discussion of acceptability of proposed new foods,
medicines, etc. among potential consumers or patients.</def>⟦br⟧
